data.description: Wishing For A Home That Radiates Grace And Elegance Much Like Mediterranean Style Homes In Any Major City? One That Is Surrounded By Mature Oak Trees In A Quiet, Gated Subdivision A Short Golf Cart Ride From The McAllen Country Club?  If So, Then You Have Found Your Dream Home! This Lovely Property Is Ideal For The Traveler-At-Heart As The Bricked Courtyards At The Entrance And Off The Grand Covered Patio Offer Ease Of Maintenance And A Life Of Luxury! Custom Built With Stucco Exterior Enhanced With Hand-Crafted Cantera Accents, Separate And Marvelous Marble Baths In The Primary Suite, Luxe Marble And Travertine Flooring In The Entertaining Spaces, An Expansive Open-Concept Combination Of Family Room, Breakfast And Kitchen For Gathering Friends And Family, Grand Windows Providing An Abundance Of Natural Light, An Over-Sized Three-Car Garage With Paved Flooring, And So Very Much More!!  Please View The Virtual Tour And List Of Amenities For Additional Details. Enjoy!
